%% Event processing (outbox). See 08-event-and-workflow-architecture.md
flowchart LR
  Producer[Domain action\nemit(event) with tenantId envelope] --> Sync{sync?}
  Sync -- money/approval --> Inproc[in-process consumer\nidempotent]
  Sync -- async --> Outbox[(t:tid:outbox)]
  Outbox --> Drain[Cron outbox drainer]
  Drain --> C1[Notifications]
  Drain --> C2[AI actions]
  Drain --> C3[Analytics read-model]
  Drain --> C4[Audit]
  Drain --> Retry{success?}
  Retry -- no, attempts<N --> Backoff[backoff -> re-enqueue]
  Backoff --> Outbox
  Retry -- no, attempts>=N --> Dead[(t:tid:outbox:dead)] --> Alert[owner alert + admin UI]
  Retry -- yes --> Done[ack]
